f\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533965\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533965\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xxg1665702796648.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xxg1665702796648.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xxg1665702796648.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xxg1665702796648\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Resource Browser: Snippets\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Insert, copy or paste code snippets from Snippet Libraries into your script or layout.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__p_d5600e1_d5601e1_d5602e1\">Uniface provides the default\n\t\tlibraries for HTML and ProcScript:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__li_d2720e1_d2721e1_d2722e1\">UHTML_COMMON—HTML snippets for server page layouts</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__li_d2723e1_d2724e1_d2725e1\">USCRIPT_COMMON—common Script snippets</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__li_d2726e1_d2727e1_d2728e1\">USCRIPT_API—trigger snippets for application shells</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__li_d2729e1_d2730e1_d2731e1\">USCRIPT_<var class=\"keyword varname\">CPT</var>—trigger snippets for specific component types</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__note_w29ab1b7b5_w30ab1b7_w31ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> USYSLIBSNP is the template for snippet libraries.\n      </div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__section_hsf_3s2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d369347e79\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__ul_vcg_ks2_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__li_d2732e1_d2733e1_d2734e1\">To select a snippet library, click\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">libsnp</code> in the U-Bar of the Resource Browser, and select the\n               library you want to use.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__li_d2735e1_d2736e1_d2737e1\">To insert a snippet, select a snippet and\n               right-click in either the Resource Browser or the code editor and use the menu to\n               insert or copy and paste snippets in the desired location.<p class=\"p\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__p_d5606e1_d5607e1_d5608e1\">If you select and copy multiple snippets, their\n                  content is pasted with a line feed separating the different snippets.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xxg1665702796648__li_d2738e1_d2739e1_d2740e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hpl1704450799621.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hpl1704450799621.html\" title=\"You can find and insert snippets using the Snippet tab of the Resource Browser in the Write Script worksheet.\">Find and Insert Snippets</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/biv1704450635249.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Snippets</a><p>Snippets are named fragments of code or text that you can insert into your application script or layout to speed development. They are defined as development objects in snippet libraries.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533965\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533965\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Resource Browser: Snippets Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Resource Browser: Snippets Insert, copy or paste code snippets from Snippet Libraries into your script or layout. Uniface provides the default libraries for HTML and ProcScript: UHTML_COMMON—HTML snippets for server page layouts USCRIPT_COMMON—common Script snippets USCRIPT_API—trigger snippets for application shells USCRIPT_ CPT —trigger snippets for specific component types Note: USYSLIBSNP is the template for snippet libraries. How to To select a snippet library, click libsnp in the U-Bar of the Resource Browser, and select the library you want to use. To insert a snippet, select a snippet and right-click in either the Resource Browser or the code editor and use the menu to insert or copy and paste snippets in the desired location. If you select and copy multiple snippets, their content is pasted with a line feed separating the different snippets. Find and Insert Snippets Related Links Snippets Snippets are named fragments of code or text that you can insert into your application script or layout to speed development. They are defined as development objects in snippet libraries. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}